{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/spring-wedding-guest-outfit-men-inspiration/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"The Runway Wire: The Blog of Runway Rewards Shop"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"ac292146-3f74-508c-90e2-5c25f8f4b113","excerpt":"Welcome to the season of love, new beginnings, and some stunning fashion choices! Spring is heralded as one of the most beautiful times of the year and is also…","html":"<p>Welcome to the season of love, new beginnings, and some stunning fashion choices! Spring is heralded as one of the most beautiful times of the year and is also a popular season for weddings. The renewal of life, the color riot in nature’s palette, and the pleasant weather all come together to create a romantic ambiance, perfect for tying the knot. If you’re attending a wedding this spring, your outfit will play a major role in making a statement. Don't worry; we've got you covered with some fantastic outfit inspiration to help you dazzle as a guest at any spring wedding.</p>\n<h1>The Charm of Casual Elegance</h1>\n<p>Spring weddings often take advantage of the season’s fabulous weather, with many being hosted outside in beautiful gardens or on sunny beaches. For such occasions, steering towards the relaxed side of fashion while retaining a dash of elegance will score you major style points<sup id=\"fnref-1^\"><a href=\"#fn-1^\" class=\"footnote-ref\">1^</a></sup>.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b043250266f46ddb6cdb2883e3203c53/72e01/image1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"A man in a well-tailored light beige suit, a pastel blue shirt without a tie and loafers\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b043250266f46ddb6cdb2883e3203c53/828fb/image1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b043250266f46ddb6cdb2883e3203c53/ff44c/image1.jpg 158w,\n/static/b043250266f46ddb6cdb2883e3203c53/a6688/image1.jpg 315w,\n/static/b043250266f46ddb6cdb2883e3203c53/828fb/image1.jpg 630w,\n/static/b043250266f46ddb6cdb2883e3203c53/0ede0/image1.jpg 945w,\n/static/b043250266f46ddb6cdb2883e3203c53/72e01/image1.jpg 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Consider a well-tailored light beige suit that resonates with the colors of the season. Pair it with a pastel blue shirt (sans tie) for added coolness. Polish off the look with a pair of loafers - equal parts stylish and comfortable for those outdoor ceremonies<sup id=\"fnref-3^\"><a href=\"#fn-3^\" class=\"footnote-ref\">3^</a></sup>.</p>\n<h1>Black Tie Sophistication</h1>\n<p>Spring doesn't always mean casual. Some weddings are black-tie events, demanding a certain level of sophistication and formality<sup id=\"fnref-2^\"><a href=\"#fn-2^\" class=\"footnote-ref\">2^</a></sup>.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/662c39ef38a4b9da42f8c629a2494487/72e01/image2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"A man in an elegantly cut black tuxedo neatly paired with a crisp white shirt, a bow tie, and shiny patent leather shoes\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/662c39ef38a4b9da42f8c629a2494487/828fb/image2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/662c39ef38a4b9da42f8c629a2494487/ff44c/image2.jpg 158w,\n/static/662c39ef38a4b9da42f8c629a2494487/a6688/image2.jpg 315w,\n/static/662c39ef38a4b9da42f8c629a2494487/828fb/image2.jpg 630w,\n/static/662c39ef38a4b9da42f8c629a2494487/0ede0/image2.jpg 945w,\n/static/662c39ef38a4b9da42f8c629a2494487/72e01/image2.jpg 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>Go classic with an elegantly cut black tuxedo, neatly paired with a crisp white shirt. Choose a bow tie - the ‘black tie’ of the black-tie look - and shine those patent leather shoes well. Radiate an air of refined magnetism that is sure to turn heads.</p>\n<h1>Adding a Pop of Color</h1>\n<p>Spring is synonymous with a burst of colors, so don't shy away from incorporating some of that vibrancy into your outfit<sup id=\"fnref-1^\"><a href=\"#fn-1^\" class=\"footnote-ref\">1^</a></sup>.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1e3af78a18b93f0aedfcce3500612959/72e01/image3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"A man in a bright pink shirt under a stylish navy-blue suit, paired with a floral tie\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1e3af78a18b93f0aedfcce3500612959/828fb/image3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1e3af78a18b93f0aedfcce3500612959/ff44c/image3.jpg 158w,\n/static/1e3af78a18b93f0aedfcce3500612959/a6688/image3.jpg 315w,\n/static/1e3af78a18b93f0aedfcce3500612959/828fb/image3.jpg 630w,\n/static/1e3af78a18b93f0aedfcce3500612959/0ede0/image3.jpg 945w,\n/static/1e3af78a18b93f0aedfcce3500612959/72e01/image3.jpg 1024w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>To create a daring and refreshing spring look, consider a bright pink shirt under a stylish navy-blue suit. Break the monotony with a floral tie, adding an element of fun and festivity to your wedding guest ensemble.</p>\n<h1>Be the Talk of the Hour</h1>\n<p>\"Style is a way to say who you are without having to speak,\" fashion icon Rachel Zoe once said, and we couldn't agree more. Navigate the nuptial season in style with our spring wedding guest outfit inspirations. Don’t be a wallflower but be the talk of the hour! Remember, dressing well for a wedding goes beyond just looking good. It shows your respect for the hosts and makes the celebration all the more memorable. Be bold, be stylish - own the season of love and joy with your impeccable fashion sense.</p>\n<p>Don’t forget to share this guide with your friends and spread the fashion-forward movement this spring.</p>\n<p><strong>Sources</strong></p>\n<p>Stay ahead of the fashion curve by being updated with the latest trends. Check out our blog on <a href=\"https://www.fashionbeans.com/article/ss-mens-style-trends/\">men's spring fashion trends</a>. And if you're still unsure, check out our previous blog post on <a href=\"./the-perfect-suit.md\">the art of picking the perfect suit</a> to help guide your style choices.</p>\n<div class=\"footnotes\">\n<hr>\n<ol>\n<li id=\"fn-1^\"><a href=\"https://hespokestyle.com/what-to-wear-spring-wedding/\">He Spoke Style, Spring Wedding Outfit Inspiration</a><a href=\"#fnref-1%5E\" class=\"footnote-backref\">↩</a></li>\n<li id=\"fn-3^\"><a href=\"https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/gallery/wedding-suits\">British GQ, Men's Fashion Tips for Wedding Season</a><a href=\"#fnref-3%5E\" class=\"footnote-backref\">↩</a></li>\n<li id=\"fn-2^\"><a href=\"https://www.esquire.com/style/mens-fashion/a27448689/what-to-wear-to-a-wedding-suits-men\">Esquire, A Guide to Men's Wedding Guest Attire</a><a href=\"#fnref-2%5E\" class=\"footnote-backref\">↩</a></li>\n</ol>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Step into Spring: Style Essentials for the Wedding Guest Man","date":null,"description":"Explore our guide on Spring Wedding Guest Outfit Inspiration for Men. Strike the right balance between relaxed chic and formal elegance this wedding season."}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring-wedding-outfit-inspiration/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Spring into Style: Wedding Guest Outfit Inspiration for the Spring Season"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/spring-wedding-guest-outfit-inspiration/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Chic and Stylish: Spring Wedding Guest Outfit Inspiration for Women"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"ac292146-3f74-508c-90e2-5c25f8f4b113","previousPostId":"84e04364-26b7-508d-b0c6-a64e4b6ccb08","nextPostId":"6f992150-a2ba-5043-9dd3-a56a5032e8a5"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"],"slicesMap":{}}